Hi Bubanee,  just thought I'd say another hello.  To be honest with you I'm a bit bored at the moment, also having sleep problems these last 2 nights, can't get to bloody sleep at night lol oh well :-(  Yeah anyway besides, it's good to see you have many torrents going at the moment.  You've got bloody loads of em haha!  Yeah unfortunately those Now ones I did got completely flushed out of the top 100.  I watched them go down over the period of weeks they did.  They seemed to do pretty well.  Got some good positive feedback from people.  Yeah I like it when people say good stuff, it's nice to hear good constructive comments.  My latest ones are doing well now, got all that weird rock stuff going and many downloaders are coming along.  Maybe not in the top 100 but still they've become quite popular so I guess that many people are listening to this weird stuff now.  I've already made just over 25 gigs so far, it's been hard work.  It takes a lot of time especially the tagging of each mp3 but I've deviced a system which I work to now.  It's good when people appreciate what you've done for them.  I'm just so impressed with how many good torrents you've got going at the moment.  This Shakira album is pretty good, no wonder it's popular.  I saw her on a UK television programme the other day called X Factor you probably know it.  She performed one of the new ones from this album and she was good, I thought better than Britney Spears, I've heard Britney has gone very downhill recently and that she don't even sing live anymore.  She's losing fans according to what I've read cause people are just giving up on her, shame really.  I hope I get to sleep tonight lol I'm becoming a night person and I want to sleep during the day but have to get up for work so it's a bit of a problem lol :-)
